        -- ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ Slider ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ
        function Tab:AddSlider(sliderConfig)
            sliderConfig = sliderConfig or {}
            local name     = sliderConfig.Name    or "Slider"
            local min      = sliderConfig.Min     or 0
            local max      = sliderConfig.Max     or 100
            local default  = sliderConfig.Default or min
            local suffix   = sliderConfig.Suffix  or ""
            local callback = sliderConfig.Callback or function() end
            local value    = math.clamp(default, min, max)

            local holder = Create("Frame", {
                Size            = UDim2.new(1, 0, 0, 58),
                BackgroundColor3 = T.SurfaceAlt,
                BorderSizePixel = 0,
                ZIndex          = 13,
                Parent          = tabPage,
            })
            RoundCorner(holder, 8)
            Create("UIStroke", { Color = T.Border, Thickness = 1, Parent = holder })

            local nameLabel = Create("TextLabel", {
                Size            = UDim2.new(1, -80, 0, 20),
                Position        = UDim2.new(0, 12, 0, 10),
                BackgroundTransparency = 1,
                Text            = name,
                TextColor3      = T.Text,
                Font            = Enum.Font.GothamSemibold,
                TextSize        = 13,
                TextXAlignment  = Enum.TextXAlignment.Left,
                ZIndex          = 14,
                Parent          = holder,
            })

            local valueLabel = Create("TextLabel", {
                Size            = UDim2.new(0, 70, 0, 20),
                Position        = UDim2.new(1, -82, 0, 10),
                BackgroundTransparency = 1,
                Text            = tostring(value) .. suffix,
                TextColor3      = T.Primary,
                Font            = Enum.Font.GothamBold,
                TextSize        = 13,
                TextXAlignment  = Enum.TextXAlignment.Right,
                ZIndex          = 14,
                Parent          = holder,
            })

            -- Track
            local trackBg = Create("Frame", {
                Size            = UDim2.new(1, -24, 0, 6),
                Position        = UDim2.new(0, 12, 0, 40),
                BackgroundColor3 = T.Border,
                BorderSizePixel = 0,
                ZIndex          = 14,
                Parent          = holder,
            })
            RoundCorner(trackBg, 3)

            local trackFill = Create("Frame", {
                Size            = UDim2.new((value - min) / (max - min), 0, 1, 0),
                BackgroundColor3 = T.Primary,
                BorderSizePixel = 0,
                ZIndex          = 15,
                Parent          = trackBg,
            })
            RoundCorner(trackFill, 3)

            -- Knob
            local knob = Create("Frame", {
                Size            = UDim2.new(0, 14, 0, 14),
                Position        = UDim2.new((value - min) / (max - min), -7, 0.5, -7),
                BackgroundColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(255, 255, 255),
                BorderSizePixel = 0,
                ZIndex          = 16,
                Parent          = trackBg,
            })
            RoundCorner(knob, 7)

            local Element = { Value = value }
            local draggingSlider = false

            local function SetValue(v, fire)
                v            = math.clamp(math.floor(v + 0.5), min, max)
                value        = v
                Element.Value = v
                local pct    = (v - min) / (max - min)
                Tween(trackFill, { Size = UDim2.new(pct, 0, 1, 0)                }, 0.05)
                Tween(knob,      { Position = UDim2.new(pct, -7, 0.5, -7)        }, 0.05)
                valueLabel.Text = tostring(v) .. suffix
                if fire ~= false then SafeCall(callback, v) end
            end

            local clickZone = Create("TextButton", {
                Size            = UDim2.new(1, 0, 0, 28),
                Position        = UDim2.new(0, 0, 0, 30),
                BackgroundTransparency = 1,
                Text            = "",
                ZIndex          = 17,
                Parent          = holder,
            })

            clickZone.InputBegan:Connect(function(input)
                if input.UserInputType == Enum.UserInputType.MouseButton1 then
                    draggingSlider = true
                end
            end)
            clickZone.InputEnded:Connect(function(input)
                if input.UserInputType == Enum.UserInputType.MouseButton1 then
                    draggingSlider = false
                end
            end)
            UserInputService.InputChanged:Connect(function(input)
                if draggingSlider and input.UserInputType == Enum.UserInputType.MouseMovement then
                    local abs  = trackBg.AbsolutePosition
                    local size = trackBg.AbsoluteSize
                    local pct  = math.clamp((input.Position.X - abs.X) / size.X, 0, 1)
                    SetValue(min + pct * (max - min))
                end
            end)

            function Element:Set(v) SetValue(v, true) end
            function Element:Get() return value end
            return Element
        end

        -- ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ Dropdown ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ‚ĒÄ
        function Tab:AddDropdown(ddConfig)
            ddConfig = ddConfig or {}
            local name     = ddConfig.Name    or "Dropdown"
            local options  = ddConfig.Options  or {}
            local default  = ddConfig.Default  or options[1]
            local callback = ddConfig.Callback or function() end
            local selected = default
            local isOpen   = false

            local holder = Create("Frame", {
                Size            = UDim2.new(1, 0, 0, 38),
                BackgroundColor3 = T.SurfaceAlt,
                BorderSizePixel = 0,
                ClipsDescendants = false,
                ZIndex          = 13,
                Parent          = tabPage,
            })
            RoundCorner(holder, 8)
            Create("UIStroke", { Color = T.Border, Thickness = 1, Parent = holder })

            Create("TextLabel", {
                Size            = UDim2.new(0.5, 0, 0, 38),
                Position        = UDim2.new(0, 12, 0, 0),
                BackgroundTransparency = 1,
                Text            = name,
                TextColor3      = T.Text,
                Font            = Enum.Font.GothamSemibold,
                TextSize        = 13,
                TextXAlignment  = Enum.TextXAlignment.Left,
                ZIndex          = 14,
                Parent          = holder,
            })

            local selectedLabel = Create("TextLabel", {
                Size            = UDim2.new(0.45, -30, 0, 38),
                Position        = UDim2.new(0.5, 0, 0, 0),
                BackgroundTransparency = 1,
                Text            = tostring(selected or "Select..."),
                TextColor3      = T.Primary,
                Font            = Enum.Font.Gotham,
                TextSize        = 12,
                TextXAlignment  = Enum.TextXAlignment.Right,
                ZIndex          = 14,
                Parent          = holder,
            })

            local arrow = Create("TextLabel", {
                Size            = UDim2.new(0, 20, 0, 38),
                Position        = UDim2.new(1, -28, 0, 0),
                BackgroundTransparency = 1,
                Text            = "‚Ėĺ",
                TextColor3      = T.TextDim,
                Font            = Enum.Font.GothamBold,
                TextSize        = 14,
                ZIndex          = 14,
                Parent          = holder,
            })

            -- Dropdown list (appears above/below)
            local dropList = Create("Frame", {
                Size            = UDim2.new(1, 0, 0, 0),
                Position        = UDim2.new(0, 0, 1, 4),
                BackgroundColor3 = T.Surface,
                BorderSizePixel = 0,
                ClipsDescendants = true,
                ZIndex          = 50,
                Visible         = false,
                Parent          = holder,
            })
            RoundCorner(dropList, 8)
            Create("UIStroke", { Color = T.Border, Thickness = 1, Parent = dropList })
            MakeListLayout(dropList, 2)
            MakePadding(dropList, 4, 4, 4, 4)

            local Element = { Value = selected }

            local function SetSelected(opt)
                selected             = opt
                Element.Value        = opt
                selectedLabel.Text   = tostring(opt)
                SafeCall(callback, opt)
            end

            local function RefreshOptions()
                for _, c in ipairs(dropList:GetChildren()) do
                    if c:IsA("TextButton") then c:Destroy() end
                end
                for _, opt in ipairs(options) do
                    local optBtn = Create("TextButton", {
                        Size            = UDim2.new(1, 0, 0, 28),
                        BackgroundColor3 = opt == selected and T.Primary or T.SurfaceAlt,
                        Text            = tostring(opt),
                        TextColor3      = opt == selected and Color3.fromRGB(255,255,255) or T.Text,
                        Font            = Enum.Font.Gotham,
                        TextSize        = 12,
                        BorderSizePixel = 0,
                        ZIndex          = 51,
                        Parent          = dropList,
                    })
                    RoundCorner(optBtn, 6)
                    optBtn.MouseEnter:Connect(function()
                        if opt ~= selected then
                            Tween(optBtn, { BackgroundColor3 = T.Border }, 0.1)
                        end
                    end)
                    optBtn.MouseLeave:Connect(function()
                        if opt ~= selected then
                            Tween(optBtn, { BackgroundColor3 = T.SurfaceAlt }, 0.1)
                        end
                    end)
                    optBtn.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
                        SetSelected(opt)
                        -- Close
                        isOpen = false
                        Tween(dropList, { Size = UDim2.new(1, 0, 0, 0) }, 0.2)
                        Tween(arrow,    { Rotation = 0                  }, 0.2)
                        task.delay(0.22, function() dropList.Visible = false end)
                    end)
                end
            end
            RefreshOptions()

            local toggleBtn = Create("TextButton", {
                Size            = UDim2.new(1, 0, 1, 0),
                BackgroundTransparency = 1,
                Text            = "",
                ZIndex          = 15,
                Parent          = holder,
            })
            toggleBtn.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
                isOpen = not isOpen
                if isOpen then
                    RefreshOptions()
                    dropList.Visible = true
                    local targetH = math.min(#options * 30 + 8, 180)
                    Tween(dropList, { Size = UDim2.new(1, 0, 0, targetH) }, 0.2, Enum.EasingStyle.Back)
                    Tween(arrow,    { Rotation = 180 }, 0.2)
                else
                    Tween(dropList, { Size = UDim2.new(1, 0, 0, 0) }, 0.2)
                    Tween(arrow,    { Rotation = 0   }, 0.2)
                    task.delay(0.22, function() dropList.Visible = false end)
                end
            end)

            function Element:Set(v) SetSelected(v) end
            function Element:Get() return selected end
            function Element:SetOptions(opts) options = opts; RefreshOptions() end
            return Element
        end

